==English==
===Etymology 1===
Shortened from ''cobbler's awls'', for ''[[ball]]s'' (testicles or nonsense)
===Noun 1===
'''cobblers'''
#(''[[Cockney rhyming slang]]'') [[Testicle]]s.
#:''Then she only goes and kicks me right in me cobblers, don't she!''<!--the incorrect grammar is illustrative and intentional-->
#(''[[Cockney rhyming slang]]'') [[Nonsense]].
#:''Stop talking cobblers.''
#(''slang'') The [[police]].
#:''Our house got broken into, but the cobblers wouldn't dust for prints.''

